.DT
query_story
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_story

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_story -  This method returns the story associated with the player.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
string query_story(string name)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^name%^RESET%^ - the player name
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the story of the player
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/library.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the story associated with the player.   This is
created from all the information about the quests they have done
joined together into a neato story.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
/handlers/quest_handler->query_quest_story()

.EP

